		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Ijazah3.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Image 8A calligraphy of prophet Muhammad&#39;s hadith regarding helping the poor Author: Ali Ra&#39;if Efendi"><img alt="Image 8A calligraphy of prophet Muhammad&#39;s hadith regarding helping the poor Author: Ali Ra&#39;if Efendi" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Ijazah3.jpg/120px-Ijazah3.jpg" decoding="async" width="120" height="88" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Ijazah3.jpg/180px-Ijazah3.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Ijazah3.jpg/240px-Ijazah3.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4801" data-file-height="3534" /></a></span></div>
