ass="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeBullet"><a class="CategoryTreeToggle" data-ct-title="Shia_organizations" aria-expanded="false"></a> </span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Shia_organizations" title="Category:Shia organizations">Shia organizations</a></div><div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div></div><div class="CategoryTreeSection"><div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeBullet"><a class="CategoryTreeToggle" data-ct-title="Shia_Islamic_holy_places" aria-expanded="false"></a> </span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Shia_Islamic_holy_places" title="Category:Shia Islamic holy places">Shia Islamic holy places</a></div><div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div></div><div class="CategoryTreeSection"><div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeBullet"><a class="CategoryTreeToggle" data-ct-title="Shia_Islam_and_politics" aria-expanded="false"></a> </span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Shia_Islam_and_politics" title="Category:Shia Islam and politics">Shia Islam and politics</a></div><div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div></div><div class="CategoryTreeSection"><div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeEmptyBullet"></span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Shia_prayers" title="Category:Shia prayers">Shia prayers</a></div><div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div></div><div class="CategoryTreeSection"><div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeBullet"><a class="CategoryTreeToggle" data-ct-title="Scholars_of_Shia_Islam" aria-expanded="false"></a> </span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Scholars_of_Shia_Islam" title="Category:Scholars of Shia Islam">Scholars of Shia Islam</a></div><div class="CategoryTreeChildren" style="display:none"></div></div><div class="CategoryTreeSection"><div class="CategoryTreeItem"><span class="CategoryTreeEmptyBullet"></span> <a href="/wiki/Category:Shi%27ite_surnames" title="Category:Shi&#39;ite surnames">Shi&#39;ite surnames</a></div><div clas