<td><div style="text-align:left; margin-bottom:0px"><b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Shia_Islam/Selected_quote" title="Portal:Shia Islam/Selected quote">More selected quotes</a></b></div></td>
<td><div style="text-align:right;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0px;"><b><a href="https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Category:Shiism" class="extiw" title="wikiquote:Category:Shiism">More...</a></b></div>
